Name: Average time from Manuscript Export Succeeded to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Total time for Plagiarism Originality Report Completed across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the end of the case

Name: Average time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total resolution time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed for manuscripts leading to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time it takes from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit for cases where this path is followed
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'total'}

Name: Average time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation in cases of major revision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time for Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in variants leading to SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-AE Assign Reviewers in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in cases ending with SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average waiting time to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Plagiarism Originality Report Completed Cycle Time in the context of manuscripts undergoing minor revision cycles
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and the end of case where activity 'SW-EIC Minor Revision occurs
